{{Top|leg}}
'''Seeking rail charges''' were red-colored, heat-seeking rail charges, designed for use with a [[Seeker Rail Detonator]]. They were somewhat rarer than average [[Rail charge]]s. This variation sought out sources of heat while in flight. In all other aspects, they acted like normal charges.

{{Weapon-stub}}

